        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>National Commission on the COVID-19 Pandemic Act</strong></p> <p>This bill temporarily establishes the National Commission on the COVID-19 Pandemic in the legislative branch to investigate the facts and circumstances regarding the emergence of, spread of, and response to COVID-19. The commission terminates 90 days after it submits a final report of its findings and recommendations.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
